{"id":364248,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":3,"day":8}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"360","ytitle":"","mtitle":"“三八”节的诗","ftitle":"","authors":["芦芒"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"芦芒　诗画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姊妹们，今天是你们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是我们的节日。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女——不比男人差，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女——比男人们强!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不信!?那就看一看西郊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明社女社长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张裕秀同志的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条臂膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可有多棒!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时代最美丽的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是开在你们的辫子上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是电焊蓝色的火光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀在钢铁上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主妇们!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，你们纤手上戴的钻戒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比不上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们劳动后手上长的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老茧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小姐们!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漂亮的服装——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是尼龙丝的柔光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是油腻的工作服上喷着芬芳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉的母亲们!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子，不只是你的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“心肝”“宝贝”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你们养大的一群雄鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让他们为祖国效劳服务"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去飞翔吧!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妻子们!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈夫是需要你的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温柔和安慰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是——更需要你督促他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在劳动岗位上永不掉队!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丈夫们!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别再像鹦哥那么老是对妻子叫着:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老婆!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嗯，小鸟，我的小鸟……!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女——是一条坚强的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们真心的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱她们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要从心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫她们一声:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“共同战斗的——同志。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\03\\5838030201.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\03\\5838030202.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\03\\5838030203.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1958\\03\\5838030204.JPG\">"}]}